title: ArcGIS Web Adaptor
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: MIT
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors web adaptors registered with an ArcGIS Server site.

 A missing web adaptor is CRIT by default because traffic routed through that
 adaptor will no longer reach the Server site. A web adaptor with admin access
 enabled is WARN by default because it exposes the ArcGIS Server Admin REST API
 through the web adaptor URL.
item:
 The web adaptor URL.
discovery:
 One service is discovered for each web adaptor returned by the Server admin API.
